  "title": "ACCOUNTS ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities and Duties</strong></p><ul><li><strong></strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=Data+Entry+%26+Bookkeeping&sca_esv=c9abda672b4293cf&sxsrf=ANbL-n6vupV_DbihbmEHlLrMe7fzxOs5fg%3A1769401657611&source=hp&ei=Oe12ab6zI6OYnesPibCxsA0&iflsig=AFdpzrgAAAAAaXb7ScTK68BHuvnTQQP-je1z6FMbF-X1&oq=job+scope+of+Accont+&gs_&sclient=gws-wiz&ved=2ahUKEwje1ojvrqiSAxXTUGwGHXOAIGkQgK4QegYIAAgAEAg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong></strong></a><strong>Data Entry, recording daily financial transactions, updating ledgers, and maintaining accurate,\nup-to-date records.</strong></li><li><strong></strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=Accounts+Payable%2FReceivable&sca_esv=c9abda672b4293cf&sxsrf=ANbL-n6vupV_DbihbmEHlLrMe7fzxOs5fg%3A1769401657611&source=hp&ei=Oe12ab6zI6OYnesPibCxsA0&iflsig=AFdpzrgAAAAAaXb7ScTK68BHuvnTQQP-je1z6FMbF-X1&oq=job+scope+of+Accont+&gs_&sclient=gws-wiz&ved=2ahUKEwje1ojvrqiSAxXTUGwGHXOAIGkQgK4QegYIAAgAEAo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong></strong></a><strong>Processing invoices, expense reports, and payments, while also chasing debt and\nmanaging client/vendor inquiries.</strong></li><li><strong></strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=Reconciliation+%26+Reporting&sca_esv=c9abda672b4293cf&sxsrf=ANbL-n6vupV_DbihbmEHlLrMe7fzxOs5fg%3A1769401657611&source=hp&ei=Oe12ab6zI6OYnesPibCxsA0&iflsig=AFdpzrgAAAAAaXb7ScTK68BHuvnTQQP-je1z6FMbF-X1&oq=job+scope+of+Accont+&gs_&sclient=gws-wiz&ved=2ahUKEwje1ojvrqiSAxXTUGwGHXOAIGkQgK4QegYIAAgBEAE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong></strong></a><strong>Reconciling bank statements, checking accuracy in financial reports, and assisting\nwith audits.</strong></li><li><strong></strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=Administrative+Support&sca_esv=c9abda672b4293cf&sxsrf=ANbL-n6vupV_DbihbmEHlLrMe7fzxOs5fg%3A1769401657611&source=hp&ei=Oe12ab6zI6OYnesPibCxsA0&iflsig=AFdpzrgAAAAAaXb7ScTK68BHuvnTQQP-je1z6FMbF-X1&oq=job+scope+of+Accont+&gs_&sclient=gws-wiz&ved=2ahUKEwje1ojvrqiSAxXTUGwGHXOAIGkQgK4QegYIAAgCEAE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong></strong></a><strong>Administrative support, filing documents, handling emails/calls, and assisting with payroll or budgetary tasks. </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Required Skills and Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><strong>A postsecondary certificate, associate degree, or bachelor’s degree in accounting or finance is typically preferred.</strong></li><li><strong>Strong analytical, mathematical, and organizational skills.</strong></li><li><strong>Previous experience in clerical, or administrative roles is often required. </strong></li></ul>",
